Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Bunawan Central Elementary School in the City of Davao to Daniel M. Perez Central Elementary School

BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 666
An Act Changing the Name of the Bunawan Central Elementary School in the City of Davao to Daniel M. Perez Central Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Bunawan Central Elementary School in the City of Davao is changed to Daniel M. Perez Elementary School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
